# Large data files that should NOT be committed via plain git
# (use Zenodo for these):
#   results/test_suite/sNN__*/  — per-run nested-sampling chains (~100 MB each)
#   results/GW170817_GWTC-1.hdf5  — LVK reference HDF5
# The smaller summary CSVs (results/test_suite/*.csv directly under test_suite/)
# remain committed because their typical size is ~1 KB.
results/test_suite/s[0-9]*__*/
results/GW170817_GWTC-1.hdf5
results/**/IGWN-GWTC2p1-v2-*.h5
